title: X-Men - The Twelve Storyline
description:
In an attempt to gain godhood, Apocalypse gathers twelve powerful mutants, called (originally) the Twelve. His plan, to take their powers and transfer them to himself! Who are the twelve and can the X-Men stop him?

Pack contains the leading up issues, as well as nine issue The Twelve storyline and reading order index;

Astonishing X-Men v2 01-03.
Cable 75-76
The New Eternals - Apocalypse Now
The Uncanny X-Men 372-377
Wolverine 145-147
X-Man 59-60
X-Men 92-97

This leads directly into The Ages of Apocalypse. 


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
